; NAME:
;       SCREENJPEG
; PURPOSE:
;       Display a jpeg image in a screen window.
; CATEGORY:
; CALLING SEQUENCE:
;       screenjpeg, [file]
; INPUTS:
;       file = name of JPEG file.   in
; KEYWORD PARAMETERS:
; OUTPUTS:
; COMMON BLOCKS:
; NOTES:
;       Notes: Prompts for file if called with no args.
